<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>

  <body style="font-family: sans-serif">
    <header>
      <div
        style="
          width: 100%;
          display: flex;
          height: 60px;
          background-color: #202020;
          color: white;
          font-size: 18px;
          font-weight: bold;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          text-align: center;
        "
      >
        <h style="position: relative">
          ALL-CON<br />
          비밀번호 찾기 메일입니다.
        </h>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          background-color: #ffce63;
          width: 100%;
          height: 8px;
          margin-bottom: 30px;
        "
      ></div>
    </header>

    <section>
      <article
        style="
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          width: 60%;
          max-width: 1500px;
          height: 350px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          margin-bottom: 70px;
          margin-top: 70px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          background-color: #f5f5f5;
          border: 1px solid #c4c4c4;
          border-radius: 10px;
        "
      >
        <%=confirmNumber %>
      </article>
    </section>
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 8px; background-color: #ffce63"></div>
    <footer
      style="
        font-size: 14px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #202020;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
      "
    >
      <div style="margin-bottom: 10px">
        <a
          href="https://all-con.kr"
          style="
            display: block;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-decoration: none;
          "
          ><img style="height: 70px" src="<%" ="allconLogo" % /> /></a
        >
      </div>
      <p>Copyright ⓒ 2021-2022 weAct. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px">
        본 메일은 발신전용입니다.<br />문의사항이 있으시다면
        <a
          href="https://github.com/codestates/ALL-CON"
          style="text-decoration: none; color: #ffce63"
          >ALL-CON Github</a
        >를 확인해주세요.
      </p>
      <br />
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center">
        <img
          style="height: 30px; margin-right: 20px; top: 10px"
          src="<%"
          ="youtubeLogo"
          %
        />
        /> <img style="height: 30px; top: 10px" src="<%" ="instaLogo" % /> />
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
